```cpp
class Solution {
public:
    long long maximumTripletValue(vector<int>& nums, int fir) {
        long long res = 0;
        for(int i = fir+1; i+1 < nums.size(); ++i){
            res = max(res, (long long)(nums[fir] - nums[i]) * (*max_element(nums.begin()+i+1, nums.end())));
        }
        return res;
    }

    long long maximumTripletValue(vector<int>& nums) {
        long long res = 0;
        for(int i = 0; i+2 < nums.size(); ++i){
            res = max(res, maximumTripletValue(nums, i));
        }
        return res;
    }
};
```

```cpp
class Solution {
private:
    int best_2nd, best_3rd;

public:
    long long maximumTripletValue(vector<int>& nums, int fir) {
        if(best_2nd > fir){
            // previous best choice is suitable for this fir
            long long val = (long long)(nums[fir] - nums[best_2nd]) * nums[best_3rd];
            return val;
        }

        long long res = 0;
        for(int i = fir+1; i+1 < nums.size(); ++i){
            auto it = max_element(nums.begin()+i+1, nums.end());
            long long val = (long long)(nums[fir] - nums[i]) * (*it);

            if(val >= res){
                res = val;
                best_2nd = i;
                best_3rd = it-nums.begin();
            }
        }
        return res;
    }

    long long maximumTripletValue(vector<int>& nums) {
        best_2nd = 0;
        best_3rd = 0;
        long long res = 0;
        for(int i = 0; i+2 < nums.size(); ++i){
            res = max(res, maximumTripletValue(nums, i));
        }
        return res;
    }
};
```
